sentence: The use of 1,4-butanediol as an intelligent cosubstrate has also been validated in non-aqueous media using a commercial Alcohol dehydrogenase .Kara S, Spickermann D, Weckbecker A, Leggewie C, Arends IWCE, Hollmann F (2014) Bioreductions Catalyzed by an Alcohol Dehydrogenase in Non-aqueous Media.
